titles.title: To designate the Federal building in Jacksonville, Florida, as the "Charles E. Bennett Federal Building".

bill.summary: 6/16/1993--Introduced. Designates the Federal building at 400 Bay Street, Jacksonville, Florida (or any building built to replace it), as the Charles E. Bennett Federal Building.
